Actor Yul Edochie has began trending online once again after he shared a video about his marriage to two women. The actor revealed that getting married to his second wife has brought him blessings, and it has also elevated his career. It now appears that his daughter, Danielle Edochie has been tagged severally to posts relating to her father, Yul, who is currently trending on several social media platforms.
She shared a post on her Instagram story, and Instablog9ja has now shared the post on their blog. Danielle begged people to stop trying to force acting on her. She clearly stated that she is not an actress, and she is not interested in Nollywood. She then begged people to stop tagging her to posts related to her father, Yul Edochie.
According to her, acting is for her father and she is a whole different person. She also stated that she has her own identity. Check out the post below.
After the post was shared on Instablog9ja, several people have left comments, and shared their opinions on what Danielle posted.
